T* (Abstract) Tj
T* (We report on an eighteen-month migration of a municipal records system from a CRUD) Tj
T* (architecture to event sourcing.) Tj
T* (The case covers data backfill, auditability requirements, and the organisational change) Tj
T* (needed to sustain the new model.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Keywords: event sourcing, legacy migration, case study, public sector) Tj
